Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:13.59,Sign,,0,0,0,,{もうひとりの私が}There is one more, another me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:21.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,{心の奥に生きているの}The one that keeps on living in the depths of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:28.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,{空夢のように}Just like a childish fruitless{/empty} dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:34.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,{ひとりじゃないよと}"You are no longer alone" -
