Comment: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:03.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{chapter}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:13.24,Sign,,0,0,0,,A miserable romance {可哀想ね　ロマンス}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:16.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,A tear-jerking nuance {涙誘うニュアンス}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.70,0:22:20.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,If you turn another page of your memories, {想い出のページめくれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:23.33,Sign,,0,0,0,,Here she is - heroine of the past {追憶のヒロイン} {actually, "the heroine of the recollections" but that doesn't have a nice ring to it}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:34.97,Sign,,0,0,0,,I raise my eyes to your face - {あなたの面影　見上げて咲いている}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:38.73,Sign,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, I'm in full bloom {unsure, maybe "it's flourishing"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:42.27,Sign,,0,0,0,,A sunflower amidst the blizzard - {act. in the middle of winter}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:45.67,Sign,,0,0,0,,that would be me, my dear {真冬のひまわり　それが私なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:48.84,Sign,,0,0,0,,Always on the verge of freezing, {凍えるような気持ちでいつも}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:52.24,Sign,,0,0,0,,My feelings are out of control -
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:56.79,Sign,,0,0,0,,Too stiff to even say "Do you still love me?" {「好き?」と尋くこともできず}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:23:00.94,Sign,,0,0,0,,My lips just keep wavering in this wind! {風に揺れていたわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,A pitiful Romance {いじらしいね　ロマンス}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:09.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,Something that only happens in dreams: {夢のような出来事}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:13.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,Trying hard to forget, I fell even more in love {忘れるために愛したの}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:15.95,Sign,,0,0,0,,with heroine of the past {追憶のヒロイン}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:20.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,Miracle that I came across now is hugging me tight {めぐりあえた奇跡　そっと抱きしめて}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:24.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,This is the story of my life, I'll do my best to protect it! {私だけの歴史　守ってゆくわ}
