Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,An exemplary student, Lotte \Nsurprised everyone by scoring 100 on a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In turn, the hoyden Luise \Nnearly started a brawl in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The two may have switched places, \Nbut they are still to get used to their new roles. {/they get in a lot of incidents}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:09.72,Sign,,0,0,105,,{\c&HEAFCF9&\bord0\blur0.8\fs20}Episode 8 \N {\fs35} Dad's Birthday \N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N {\fs23} \h Translation: Perevodildo | Timings: Sub-RoRo\h
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Resi, I was checking housekeeping account book here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! You can't be playing \Nwith a housekeeping account book. {unsure, maybe she means "young lady should not concern herself with ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked the account for this month only, \Nbut the calculations are already largely off. {/there are many cases of calculations not meeting}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm diligently updating it day after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... {for example}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For today's shopping, \Nyou allocated 50 schilling for vegetables, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Liquid detergent - 20 schillings 40 groschens. {detergent; cleanser; cleaning agent; washing materia}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat - 5 schillings 30 groschens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, even if we add Peperl's food expenses...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,About 10 shillings of change are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, well... I'm pretty sure \NI didn't get any change back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Resi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it those candies \Nare what became of the change?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Terribly sorry, Young Fraulein...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On nearly every page, \NResi, your cooking expenses are overblown. {unsure what she means: since then, it seems resi is spending too much on cooking}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, adding up figures {in budget}\Nand keeping a housekeeping account book -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,all the pecuniary matters I will supervise personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,May I add, Young Fraulein \Nhad never been that meticulous before. {properly; accurately; exactly; precisely; regularly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Resi. Seeing how you depend on it, \NI will allocate some budget on snacks for you. A plentiful. {/include mid-afternoon (around 3 o'clock) snack; afternoon refreshment; afternoon tea​ in the ... }
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks you very much! \NA plentiful of gratitude from me! {/please do the tappuri}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, a plentiful for Peperl, too. \NRest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you're back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Needed to collect some scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll make you some tea now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no need. I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he going out for a date with that woman again? {today}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NSuch a disheartened look. {frankly no clue what's that meoni/nyuni part}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm here, Luise, is there anything \Nyou wanted to tell me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? No, I don't have anything to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I see. Some other time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Luise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Take care, but only after I kiss you." {/I thought I'd kiss him while saying ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be able to say that. {/I can't after all}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I spend my whole life \Nliving with mother, up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't a clue how would dad react \Nif I try to kiss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been a week already since I've arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Frau Irene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Herr Palfy, fancy a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I could give you a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your whole being says "deep in thought."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something about my daughter Luise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she was before, she'd invariably \Ncuddle me and give me a kiss, whenever I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But these days, nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She didn't do it even today, on my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In all the previous years, \Nshe'd be sure to come to atelier in the morning, {to go uninvited; to call on without an invitation; to barge in on; to gatecrash}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,hands full of presents and bouquets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And today..?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have somehow \Nfallen into Luise's disfavor? {/earned hatred}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you lucky to be a grown-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can even sleep until the noon. {/adults are happy, they are stuff that sleeps until noon}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa! Can I not redeem myself \Neven by the fact I was working until late?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no sway even over my own sleep! {unsure what she means: not letting the mom sleep, maybe "it's your job to wake me up" or "it was you who didn't let me sleep until late"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy enough to just know \Nyou'd be home when I return from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The evening shift should be made a norm! {unsure what she means: I wish you'd always come to work late - maybe her mother now works eveningh shifts or idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This may happen elsewhere, \Nbut certainly not in our magazine! {/our company is not that sweet/spoiled for that}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll have to leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you wash this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you off{ to the street}. {/will come with you to the ground floor}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what day it is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late for sports day, \Ntoo soon for Christmas matinee. {athletic meet (esp. at a school); sports day; field day ... recital (i.e. of music, by a pupil) - no clue what's the latter}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What day is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of a friend of mine! \NAnyway, good luck with your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Herr Postman! \NAny General Delivery letters from Vienna?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There are, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The second one in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world might be sending those?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't tell! {/secret}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye! See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise, there is something \Nwe totally need to discuss directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,On the seventh, at two o'clock sharp, \NI want you to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This would be the time \Nwhen I and only I will be there to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,On the seventh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Today... Today at two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shucks! Two o'clock is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A call from Luise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraulein, I need to mop the room, \N so I'd like you to wait outside for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Resi, can't you mop somewhere else for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere else is mopped already. {/went there before}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But how about the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,While Resi is in the room, \NI can't talk to Luise on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, but what if you take Peperl on a walk outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's something only you ever do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, Peperl is beside himself \Nabout going out with Resi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My, the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of this! \NA nice walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte... You're Lotte, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, great! \NGreat, I finally got to hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still been a little over a week\Nbut it feels like ages had passed already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than ever! Mom was just like Lotte described her: \Nvery kind and with a great perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Also a bit feather-headed, just like I am! {careless person; scatterbrain; birdbrain; hasty person}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Dad has a mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I was afraid you also don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really a woman other than mom that dad loves?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears, he enjoys her company a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when he's there with you? {/and what about spending time with lotte?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,not been out with dad yet, because he is always busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He spends most of the time in atelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to say, you spend all this time on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This lousy dad gives more love to some broad \Nand to his work than to his Lotte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's beyond outrageous! {/unforgivable}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Luise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, you need to take a decisive action! \NLike celebrating dad's birthday, for instance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you celebrated yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,His birthday... is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget to tell you aforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, I've only been celebrating mom's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I get to take part in dad's birthday, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, for the first time, you do. {no clue what she means}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! And I have a fantastic plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fantastic plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We will both celebrate dad birthday, \Nin two different places!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Both in Munich and in Vienna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In Munich and in Vienna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting simultaneously, at six tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds incredibly fun! \NI'm in, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? \NIt's a promise! At six! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She sounded might ecstatic. \NI hope it all goes fine. {to make merry; to be ecstatic; to be in high spirits}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your purchase!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My, Luise, is there a carnival in the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Herr Strobl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good Lord, I can't even see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, that excitement does wonders to your little face. {/becoming more and more a pretty lady, don't you}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor's beard is also handsome today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something only Luise could say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was on my way to the Opera House. \NWant me to say something to your dad while I'm there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's just what I needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you give him the letter \Nfrom my left pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,An invitation, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! We've met in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Now, let's do one final rehearsal \Nfrom the very first act.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask, Frau, \Nif you could pass this to Palfy after he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alley-hop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how do you like this, Peperl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish I could show it to Luise, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years' worth of birthdays \Nthat we spent apart... {/until now, we couldn't do it together - 10 years of birthdays}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,are all getting repaired in a single evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time for us to change. \NDad should be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, congratulations on your birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte and dad are probably \Nhaving a party right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they're getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Herr Palfy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Frau Irene? \NYou've been waiting all this time? {lit: until now, here}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it was still just a rehearsal, \Nthis performance is spellbinding already! {I even got out of my seat to clap.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no need, no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans \Nfor the rest of the evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, guess I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My, sublime! \NI'm free as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, care to accompany me for a dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, with big pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.78,Sign,,0,0,0,,Imperial Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Something bothers you still? {guess, no clue what's this question}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you see... \NI just can get Luise out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, she's definitely hiding something from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, it started with her \Ngoing to the summer camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In some bizarre way, \NI think, I may just know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl's feelings in that age \Nare rather easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be just feeling lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My Luise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. After all, she's still a child \Nand she is having to grow up without a mother by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But then... \NLuise is yearning to have a mother, too? {to yearn for; to miss}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls depend on their mom \Nmore than on anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Herr Palfy, maybe it's just me thinking out loud, \Nbut suppose you remarry sometime about now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't that provide for the most natural way \Nto give Luise a mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also think, I probably would provide \Nfor a splendid mother myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,For this week's front cover, \NI'm considering one of those three portraits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless someone here can think of a better one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, today is that man's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean to say dad gives more love to that woman \N and to his work, than to his Lotte? {no clue why she says ,ore than lotte here, must be that it's a recollection in lotte's mind }
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Remarry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My, this dress is ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg a thousand pardons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is something Herr Strobl entrusted me with \Nwhile you were busy rehearsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:17:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, world's most spectacular birthday party \Ntakes place tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to witness it in atelier at six.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,At six?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Good Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies, I am urgently needed elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, give her whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Herr Palfy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My, this is scandalous! \NHe values this little shrimp more than me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And just as I was starting to get somewhere! {/I was one step away}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you to forgive him for the clamor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Frau Gerlach, your purse! {/bag}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute to Herr Palfy. Young Fraulein...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it... \NI knew it that you'd come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guilty for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You most certainly can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The most precious kiss in the world, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, dad's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bristle is spiky! {/hurts}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte and Dad's party, \NI hope it went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend that had a birthday today, \Nwho was it, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Ilse's. \NWell, goodnight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And good luck with your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought. Lotte cannot possibly know \Nit's her father's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise, can I ask just one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's about time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you finally let me know what happened \Nin the summer camp to cause such a change in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I met someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who might it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Some girl who has been growing up without a mom. \NWe argued first, but quickly became best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That alone has been enough to turn you \Ninto a diligent girl that loves cooking? {/more quiet than before and made you do cooking}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This sheds light on the entire conundrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Through an encounter with another girl like her, Luise realised \Nhow important it is to have a mother in the house. {/for luise it was enough to meet ... to change completely}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, she really yearns for mother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. \NI nearly blew it. {/it looked like I'm in trouble}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise has been feeling lonely, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So Irene was right all the way through, \NI might just need to start looking for a new mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but who could have thought \Nthat woman is actually so much into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how is he doing by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet, still as much a woman magnet as ever, \Nand still drooling when you spot a good one. {sexy; popular; well-liked​ ... to have a lewd look on one's face; to ogle​}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Ah, no. Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Soothed by the long-awaited success \Nin getting along with dad, {lit: inside dad's heart, setting aside; leaving to one side - no clue what he means, I'd suggest "in dad's heart, concern for louise finally subsided" but in the next line, it's lotte who is suddenly active role of the sentence, maybe it's still the case, just the narrator calls her lotte cause he knows; either way, it'll be too difficult to wrap in english}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte's mind is engulfed completely in gentle dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for the first time in life, she is able \Nto embrace her dad's warmth with all her heart. {very convoluted, I'm not entirely sure who is doing what annd how in that sentence}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:29.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,In the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.71,0:23:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We two have switched places!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, I'm seriously in trouble! \NI'd never tell becoming Lotte would be that hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easier for me, Luise!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cooking and cooking, day after day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be able to cook as good as Lotte, \Nor get that good scores on a test!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.33,0:23:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! At least try!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.50,0:23:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter! If you want to be \Nwith your dear dad again, you'll endure it!
